== Reliable tests

Each class grants access to a list of reliable tests. 
When the test you attempt is related to the definition of that reliable test, it applies. 
When you attempt a test, you can reroll until each die is at least equal to a minimum number. ex reroll 1 and 2. 

Overall list of reliable tests

Physical strength
Speed and agility
Stamina and resolve
Reasoning and knowledge 
Insight and influence
Bravery and persuasion
Stealth and duplicity
Perception
Authority and coercion

or other twists: 
Sacrifice and selfnessness 
Wisdom and self control

... others that fit a special class fantasy. 
Ex Wizard "Withstand hostile magical effects."

